headline: Energy Deal Creates Technical Bullish Signal for Meta Platforms Stock (META)
summary: From a fundamental perspective, social media and technology juggernaut Meta Platforms (META) recently made a compelling case for long-term investment. Meta recently entered into a 20-year power purchase agreement with Constellation Energy’s (CEG) Clinton nuclear plant in Illinois.
